  <brief_title>Riociguat Clinical Effects Studied in Patients With Insufficient Treatment Response to Phosphodiesterase-5 Inhibitor</brief_title>
  <acronym>RESPITE</acronym>
  <official_title>An Open-label, International, Multicenter, Single-arm, Uncontrolled, Phase IIIb Study of Riociguat in Patients With Pulmonary Arterial Hypertension (PAH) Who Demonstrate an Insufficient Response to Treatment With Phosphodiesterase-5 Inhibitors (PDE-5i)</official_title>
